3dslibris Licensing Overview
============================

This repository contains `3dslibris` source code together with MuPDF-based
document rendering components.

Licensing in this tree is therefore split into two layers:

1. Base project code and inherited `dslibris`-derived portions remain under
   their original `GNU GPL v2 or later` grant, as preserved in file headers and
   in [LICENSES/GPL-2.0-or-later.txt](LICENSES/GPL-2.0-or-later.txt).
2. Distributed builds combine that code with MuPDF, whose open-source
   edition is licensed under the `GNU Affero General Public License v3 or later`
   in [LICENSES/AGPL-3.0-or-later.txt](LICENSES/AGPL-3.0-or-later.txt).

As a result, the distributed `3dslibris` application should be treated as an
`AGPL v3 or later` combined work. Preserve the original file-level notices for
GPL-covered code, and comply with the corresponding-source and notice
obligations described in:

- [THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md](THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md)
- [docs/PDF_SOURCE_RELEASE.md](docs/PDF_SOURCE_RELEASE.md)

This file is a repository-level licensing guide. It does not remove or replace
license notices embedded in individual source files or vendored third-party
components.
